| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `index.ts` | Extension entry point — event handlers, commands, shortcuts |
| `types.ts` | All shared TypeScript types |
| `cookies.ts` | Firefox cookies.sqlite reader |
| `git.ts` | Async git status/remote/last-commit |
| `providers/shared.ts` | `fetchWithAuth()`, `readAuth()`, auth readers, `FetchError` |
| `providers/codex.ts` | Codex (OpenAI) quota fetcher |
| `providers/anthropic.ts` | Anthropic (Claude) quota fetcher |
