| `providers/wafer.ts` | Wafer quota fetcher |
| `providers/opencode.ts` | OpenCode quota fetcher |
| `render/header.ts` | Session-start header (ASCII art + gradient) |
| `render/footer.ts` | Multi-line footer renderer (4 lines: identity, metrics+quota, session+statuses+speed, hint) |
| `render/format.ts` | Width helpers, chips, bars, color logic, icons |
| `render/context.ts` | Context window display, incremental session totals |
| `render/pi-tui-shim.ts` | Re-exports `visibleWidth`/`truncateToWidth` from pi-tui |
